Hier is de simpelste manier om de ADC te lezen:

```c
uint32_t waarde = 0;

// In je while(1) loop:
HAL_ADC_Start(&hadc1);
HAL_ADC_PollForConversion(&hadc1, HAL_MAX_DELAY);
waarde = HAL_ADC_GetValue(&hadc1);
HAL_ADC_Stop(&hadc1);

HAL_Delay(500);
```

Dat is alles. 3 stappen:
1. **Start** de ADC
2. **Wacht** tot hij klaar is
3. **Lees** de waarde

De waarde in `waarde` is een getal tussen **0 en 4095** (12-bit ADC).

Je hebt al UART2 geconfigureerd. Voeg `sprintf` + `HAL_UART_Transmit` toe om de waarde te printen:

```c
while (1)
{
    char buffer[50];

    HAL_ADC_Start(&hadc1);
    HAL_ADC_PollForConversion(&hadc1, HAL_MAX_DELAY);
    waarde = HAL_ADC_GetValue(&hadc1);
    HAL_ADC_Stop(&hadc1);

    sprintf(buffer, "ADC: %lu\r\n", waarde);
    HAL_UART_Transmit(&huart2, (uint8_t*)buffer, strlen(buffer), HAL_MAX_DELAY);

    HAL_Delay(500);
}
```

Vergeet ook `#include <string.h>` bovenaan te zetten (voor `strlen`).

Dan in je serial monitor instellen op **38400 baud** (want dat is wat `huart2` gebruikt).

Je moet `waarde` declareren bovenaan je `main` functie. Voeg dit toe in het `/* USER CODE BEGIN 1 */` blok:

```c
/* USER CODE BEGIN 1 */
uint32_t waarde = 0;
/* USER CODE END 1 */
```

En voeg ook de benodigde includes toe:

```c
/* USER CODE BEGIN Includes */
#include <stdio.h>
#include <string.h>
/* USER CODE END Includes */
```

Brief fix: your file has one syntax error and the ADC read loop is already almost correct.\* Remove the stray `'` after `#include <string.h>`.\* Keep polling ADC once per second and store the digital value.

Use this in `main`:

```c/* USER CODE BEGIN Includes */
#include <stdio.h>
#include <string.h>
/* USER CODE END Includes */

int main(void)
{
 /* USER CODE BEGIN1 */
 uint32_t waarde =0;
 /* USER CODE END1 */

 HAL_Init();
 SystemClock_Config();
 MX_GPIO_Init();
 MX_USART2_UART_Init();
 MX_ADC1_Init();

 while (1)
 {
 HAL_ADC_Start(&hadc1);
 HAL_ADC_PollForConversion(&hadc1, HAL_MAX_DELAY);
 waarde = HAL_ADC_GetValue(&hadc1);
 HAL_ADC_Stop(&hadc1);

 HAL_Delay(1000);
 }
}
```

This uses the required HAL sequence:`HAL_ADC_Start` \-> `HAL_ADC_PollForConversion` \-> `HAL_ADC_GetValue` \-> `HAL_ADC_Stop`, every1 second.

